description:
➤ Revelation : the Bride, the Beast and Babylon for Free - https://www.amazingfacts.org/media-library/media/e/14008/t/revelation---the-bride--the-beast-and-babylon
➤ Revelation Mystery Website - https://www.revelationmystery.com

The book of Revelation tells of a battle against truth that’s leading millions into darkness. But the light refuses to die, and it can set you free today! 

No other book in the Bible has been more misrepresented than Revelation, confusing millions and sparking wild speculation. But that changes with “Revelation: The Bride, The Beast & Babylon.” This 90-minute documentary goes to the very heart of the apocalypse to logically decode the visions of Revelation 12 and 17 and reveal the rise of Babylon, the persecution of the bride of Christ, and the real-world identity of the beast power.

Shot at historic locations in Europe, “Revelation” features compelling interviews with respected theologians and historians.
